{"tid":1624020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要】謝振中張綠卡","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:46:44.000Z","uid":75782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"172c926592a93da40d76189c42372fbd9d2c0d64","tid":1624020,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人有謝蛇同佢老婆生日日期果啲詳細資料？<br />\n<br />\n佢老婆有綠卡應該係apply緊<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">F2A移民</span></span>簽證（綠卡申請配偶/未成年子女）<br />\n<br />\n最好有人爆到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢老婆個Alien Registration Number(A number)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個好緊要！！移民局係用呢個黎認人</strong></span></span><br />\n淨係得個名唔係好夠 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢地係邊個USCIS Service centre受理同埋唔知佢個case係幾時file <br />\n但F2A類簽證排期都係1年左右 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話唔定已經見左官 而家等緊綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家快手啲sd email<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果佢張綠卡批左 係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要係指定時間內人境</span></span>（2-3個月左右） 入境果時移民官先會俾張綠卡佢 大家記得留意下謝蛇幾時請左假/辭職 就算批左都要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用盡一切辦法唔俾佢入境 佢唔係限期內入境張綠卡就冇咖啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxoFwcw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxoFwcw.png&h=5c0a436e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55b08d22daf54a5ed8cfc2672be0d798d5e09800","tid":1624020,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"原Po:<br />\n<br />\n【重要】謝振中張綠卡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ed2e45930ef3108d10c5f71eabdb99046c1e6ec","tid":1624020,"uid":113902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"GPhone 唔係交左名上去喇咩<br />\n美國有心搞一個人 有名有樣就夠做喇"},{"pid":"e1cdcb56ee94b567556e6364de980f077b964792","tid":1624020,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔 #A325"},{"pid":"250fbfb16427152f8ed41f492b030a214d01a745","tid":1624020,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:43:05.000Z","msg":"推到佢冚家剷"},{"pid":"649bad6e13c7a91ac12d3bbda0b7b7c12ae982d8","tid":1624020,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"番大灣區啦 不過要唱番晒美金做人仔先用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a6d12c966166ef0f24b53d4d92e262e32a25b3","tid":1624020,"uid":24127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}